    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年4月7日-2025年4月11日）",
    "followRuleId": "1226723188126388224",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; background-color: white;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; border: 1px none windowtext;\">各位商家：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; background-color: white;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; border: 1px none windowtext;\">本周共公示9条规则，生效8条规则。</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; color: #000000; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; background-color: white;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; border: 1px none windowtext;\">具体内容如下，可点击查阅：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1226706265988796416\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台机电散热类目招商激励政策（2025.4.1-2025.6.30</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在2025年6月30日前首次成功启用且经营时间不小于30天的店铺，返还对应类目下有效销售总额的一定百分比运营支持服务费至商家钱包。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1226805716044615680\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台汽车用品类目招商激励政策（2025.4.1-2025.6.30</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">新商家在规则周期内入驻且经营（或主营）以上品类商品享受质保金优惠政策，质保金调整至1000元，无需补交；除部分特殊类目外，新商家入驻前3个自然月，费率降至1%，3个月后维持标准费率不变。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1226803954231414784\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台办公设备类目招商激励政策（2025.4.1-2025.12.31</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在激励周期内成功启用店铺且经营时长不小于2个月的商家，<span style=\"color: black;\">若自然月对应类目有效销售额达目标门槛，将返还对应类目运营支持服务费率至京东钱包。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1227853250259193856\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台五金/</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">工具类目销售激励政策（2025.4.1-2025.6.30</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在激励周期内，若店铺入驻时间&gt;3个月且店铺在五金/工具类目下有效销售额达到标准，平台将给予相应奖励，激励金返还至商家京准通账户。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1227797943176794112\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台招商管理规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整同品牌在京东招商开放平台的开店数量。品牌可以根据自身发展需要，在不同的类目下开设旗舰店，同时基于经营表现或用户体验，京东对品牌开设旗舰店的数量会进行动态评估。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1226731001624006656\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台发货管理规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #1b1b1b;\">调整关于虚拟业务、少错件、晚发赔的管理范围及标准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1090224406216708096&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">个体交易管理规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1227811979650011136\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东开放平台质保期服务规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①增加质保维修争议场景说明和处理标准：涉及无故拒绝维修场景、超时未维修/维修超时未寄回、维修费用争议、多次维修未解决、维修后争议等场景；②调整平台类目最低质保期时效。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/noticeDetail.action?id=1227874570917253120\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年五一劳动节期间延迟结算公告》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">根据清算机构关于节假日期间跨行资金清算的安排，2025年4月30日至5月5日期间的交易将在2025年5月6日统一结算。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则生效】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【新增】<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1224987876748562432&amp;btype=1\">《京东好营养-氨糖品质认证质量标准》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">明确氨糖品质认证质量标准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【新增】<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1224977882133172224&amp;btype=1\">《京东-好营养多种维生素多种矿物质片品质认证质量标准》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">明确多种维生素的品质认证质量标准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【修订】<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1223867472713748480\">《京东开放平台一物一检合规管理规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">调整一物一检酒类商品质量不合格、主观恶意逃避或躲避入仓查验以及商品假冒伪劣等其他违规行为的定义和处理措施。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">关联规则：【修订】<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1223868743667552256\">《京东开放平台个人/个体一物一检规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【修订】<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1224959652081569792\">《京东开放平台咚咚使用管理规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">①商家咚咚服务评价能力升级后，新增下线客服手动邀评能力并增强客户端防打扰能力；②新增对于商家无法满足客户购买诉求时，为客户推荐其他商家的相似商品的运营策略。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">5</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【修订】<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1224914214271979520&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台不当发布商品或信息细则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">新增<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: #f8f8f9;\">非授权第三方软件发品的违规场景和处理措施。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">关联规则：【修订】<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1224915672044277760&amp;btype=12\">《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">6</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【修订】<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1224299166499475456&amp;btype=6\">《京东开放平台拍拍二手商品质量管理通用规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0cm; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">调整原违约金档位及条款描述；新增违约场景&ldquo;商品内部物料有非厂家印章、标识、字体、石墨烯贴纸破损等（店铺防拆贴除外）&rdquo;及对应处理措施。</span></p>",
